summary: I work as a Cyber Strategy Consultant at Deloitte. As a team, we help organisations create, improve, transform, and implement their cyber strategies, which results in increased cyber security and general firm efficiency. I have a Master's degree in Management of Innovation from the Rotterdam School of Management. During my studies, as well as an internship at Erasmus consulting, I learned to perform very well under pressure. In my bachelor's degree at Leiden University, I majored in Governance, Economics and Development, which improved my strategic environment navigation and thinking. Having graduated from an international school, I come from a very international background, which comes as an advantage in most diverse environments and negotiation situations.
